those subjects. 03,15,09,11 Biology Chemistry California 18% 17% Florida 19% 3% 
Mississippi 20% 25% New York 8% 7% Sout Carolina 8% 6% North Dakota 0% 0% 
Total* 9% 8% *32 states Source: Council of Chief State School Officers 
</P>
