recently from Dallas, and he took her to lunch at the beach: 
</P>
<P>
 Admiring the sunglasses that Maggie's friend Tammy had given her, the waiter 
said to Maggie: "Great shades. Are they Liz Claiborne's?"  
</P>
<P>
 "No," Maggie replied. "Tammy gave them to me."  
