<HEADLINE>
<P>
NIBBLES AND BITS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
Compiled by Kenneth Williams 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Lynn Vogen, Kenny Wetzel, Tom Mattox and Annie Hirsch, all of Orange County, 
were named winners at Saturday's fourth annual Dance Publication's Feather 
Awards, which recognize outstanding figures in ballroom, swing and country 
dance nationwide. The awards, sponsored by Dance Action International and 
Jitterbug Magazine, both published in Laguna Beach, were presented at a 
ceremony in Beverly Hills. The show will be aired on PBS stations later this 
year. 
</P>
</TEXT>
<TYPE>
<P>
